<p>I found an interesting problem for which I'm unable to find a fix for.  Enabling the spellchecker in the RichTextBox component causes text to  disappear randomly, sometimes whilst scrolling, sometimes whilst  writing. The text is still there, it's just invisible.  The invisible text can be selected, the caret can be placed in it, and  writing causes it to become visible and sometimes the next line then  becomes invisible. The code to reproduce is quite simple, all that is  required is the RTB component with the spellchecker  enabled. I was unable to find anything similar to this problem, is this  a known issue? Is there a workaround?</p> <pre> Code to reproduce (xaml): 
